WEBVTT

00:06:27.978 --> 00:06:31.984
After winning this prize, my life changed.

00:06:31.984 --> 00:06:34.114
In the first place, people started to send me

00:06:34.114 --> 00:06:37.661
all kinds of duck-related things,

00:06:37.661 --> 00:06:40.713
and I got a real nice collection.

00:06:40.713 --> 00:06:43.040
(Laughter)

00:06:43.040 --> 00:06:49.704
More importantly,

00:06:49.704 --> 00:06:53.776
people started to send me their observations

00:06:53.776 --> 00:06:56.310
of remarkable animal behavior,

00:06:56.310 --> 00:06:59.482
and believe me, if there's an animal misbehaving on this planet,

00:06:59.482 --> 00:07:01.183
I know about it.